data.title: Inside Eagle Nation | Episode 254
data.meta_description:
1:43 It's Homecoming Week @ Georgia Southern!

2:47 Women's Soccer runs win streak to four w/triumphs over Georgia St/Southern Miss - hosts Marshall Thursday, visit JMU Sunday

3:41 Women's Rifle sets school records in air rifle, smallbore & aggregate for 3rd straight match in SoCon victory over The Citadel

4:19 Volleyball (15-4, 5-3) sweeps Marshall, heads to Georgia St Friday/Saturday

5:12 Cross Country wins GS Fall Classic

5:32 Women's Tennis hosts GS Fall Shootout - Men's Tennis competes @ ITA Regionals

6:14 Men's Soccer drops contests @ CofC/Georgia St - hosts South Carolina Wednesday

6:33 Sun Belt Basketball Media Days in New Orleans - preseason all-league teams/polls announced

8:51 Football falls 41-13 @ JMU w/post-game audio from Keaton Upshaw (10:17), Marques Watson-Trent (11:39) & head coach Clay Helton (12:39)

16:15 Brandy Clouse outlines how GS creates Breast Cancer awareness as part of Tackling for a Cure

24:19 Former GS Athletic Training student Autumn Parsons speaks of her recent diagnosis & fight w/Stage 3 Breast Cancer

43:13 Homecoming preview v ULM w/comments from head coach Terry Bowden, who was born in Douglas, GA
